Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class PartialComparisonResult

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.PartialComparisonResult
public class PartialComparisonResult
extends java.lang.Object
The result of a partial comparison using a PartialComparator.

For two partially comparable items A and B, the partial comparison result could be 'less than', 'equal', 'greater than', but also (and this is unique to partial comparisons) 'not defined'.
